parts.text:
1. "The greatest glory in living lies not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall." - Nelson Mandela


2. "The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams." - Eleanor Roosevelt


3. "It does not matter how slow you go so long as you do not stop." - Confucius


4. "If you want to live a happy life, tie it to a goal, not to people or things." - Albert Einstein


5. "The only person you are destined to become is the person you decide to be." - Ralph Waldo Emerson


6. "It's not how much you have, but how much you enjoy that makes happiness." - Charles Spurgeon


7. "The greatest wealth is to live content with little." - Plato


8. "The only way to do great work is to love what you do." - Steve Jobs


9. "Don't be afraid to fail. Be afraid not to try." - Michael Jordan


10. "The best way to predict the future is to create it." - Abraham Lincoln
